Package model

Class TerritoryDetails

java.lang.Object
model.TerritoryDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TerritoryDetails extends Object implements Serializable
All the territory details pertaining to the chosen.map file are contained in the TerritoryDetails class. It also keeps track of the nations that border it.

    • TerritoryDetails

      public TerritoryDetails(String p_index, String p_territoryId, String p_continentIndex, String p_xCoOrdinate, String p_yCoOrdinate, GameMap p_map)
      * Creates the TerritoryDetails object based on the parameters sent in. This builder is employed for reading data from ".map" files.
      Parameters:
      p_index - index in the ".map" file as per Domination's conventions
      p_territoryId - ID of the territory
      p_continentIndex - index of the continent this territory belongs to
      p_xCoOrdinate - x-coordinate on GUI map
      p_yCoOrdinate - y-coordinate on GUI map
      p_map - GameMap in which this territory resides
